::Shredder::

Shredder walks out of the CR chamber. He was fully healed an functional. He 
walks out of the ship. Megatron had left a while ago for battle, he 
remembered that. Thinking it over, he decides to sit tight for a while. He 
walks over to Anix and the speeder.

"I don't think you should bother. It's a piece of junk."
